@c help_category String Functions@Functions

@cindex searching, full-text
@cindex full-text search
@cindex FULLTEXT

@menu
* Fulltext Boolean::            Boolean Full-Text Searches
* Fulltext Query Expansion::    Full-Text Searches with Query Expansion
